sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant BA as Business Analyst
    participant UI as Angular UI
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Graph as LangGraph Pipeline
    participant RAG as ChromaDB + Ollama
    participant Claude as Claude (Anthropic)
    participant Out as ADO / Notion / Docx

    BA->>UI: Upload SDD (PDF) + PPM metadata
    UI->>API: POST /assess (multipart)
    API->>Graph: start_job(state)
    activate Graph

    Graph->>RAG: similarity_search(manuals, codebase, entities)
    RAG-->>Graph: top-k retrieved chunks

    Graph->>Claude: clarify_node(SDD + RAG context)
    Claude-->>Graph: ambiguities[]

    alt Ambiguities found
        Graph-->>API: status = clarifying
        API-->>UI: clarification_questions
        UI->>BA: Show open questions
        BA->>UI: Submit answers
        UI->>API: POST /clarify/answer/{job_id}
        API->>Graph: resume_after_clarification(answers)
    end

    Graph->>Claude: generate_node(SDD + RAG + answers)
    Claude-->>Graph: Epics, Dev Tasks, Unit Test Tasks (JSON)

    alt Review mode enabled
        Graph-->>API: status = reviewing
        API-->>UI: generated_stories
        UI->>BA: Review / edit stories
        BA->>UI: Approve stories
        UI->>API: POST /review/approve/{job_id}
        API->>Graph: resume_after_review(approved_stories)
    end

    Graph->>Out: create_ado_node / export_document_node / create_notion_node
    Out-->>Graph: work item URLs / page URLs / document path
    deactivate Graph

    Graph-->>API: status = done
    BA->>UI: Open status page
    UI->>API: GET /assess/status/{job_id}
    API-->>UI: final results
    UI-->>BA: Show Epics + links to delivered output
